= Presidential Election Candidates

With the Presidential election coming up soon, we need to decide whether to run a candidate of our own or support one from another party. Many are calling for us to make a deal with the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> to run [? if chancellor = "Marx": the current chancellor, ?][? if chancellor != "Marx": their leader, ?] Wilhelm Marx, as the unity candidate.

[? if chancellor = "Cuno": On the other hand, many in our party are calling for chancellor Wilhelm Cuno to run for presidency. ?]

Anyhow, let's see who will be the candidates on the campaign trail.

- @view_candidates_1: View the running candidates.

@view_candidates_1

